name: Devil's Roulette
summary:
♠️ The High Stakes Havoc Update is HERE!! 🃏
Experience the revamped casino stage, Casino Royale!
With updated colors and decorations, the entire arena shines brighter than ever. But don’t let the golden glow blind you!

Gold items now drop even more frequently!
The battlefield is drenched in gold, sending the chaos to a whole new level.
In this stage, everyone’s a high roller!

The new High Roller Exclusive Mega Bundle is also here,
packed with items perfect for the casino vibe!

Show your opponents...
